<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>KEIMAH PHILHLONAK AH CH208</title>
<key>D</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Kan in biak maw Bawipa, Khuaruahhar na vel ca, Nihin tiangin na kan
 huhphenh ko, Na thatnak kha kan lawmh, dong lo na dawtnak, Nangmah hmaiah
 kun in, Hmaizahnak kan in pek.

[C1]
   Nangmah na nawlbia sung bangin, Nihin ah hin, Na cabuai ah nang he
   kan i chawn, &quot;Mah hi nan tuah lai, Keimah philhlonak ah&quot; Na rak timi kha
   kan ruat than.

[V2]
 Na nunnak changreu kha, Ei awkah kan tlak lo, A til-tlawt khawmh awk
 zong kan tlak lo, Siseh nangmah thatnak, thawngin kan ra i, Na
 velngeihnak thawng in, Kannih kan i tel ve.

[C2]
   Nangmah na nawlbia sung bangin, Nihin ah hin, Na cabuai ah nang he
   kan i chawn, &quot;Mah hi nan tuah lai, Keimah philhlonak ah&quot; Na rak timi kha
   kan ruat than.

[V3]
 Kannih nih thazang thar, Ruahnak thar la u si, Zumhnak in kan hmuhmi
 thil thawng hin, Bawipa a rat than tiang, amah thihnak kha, Vancung khua
 kan phak tiangin, Langhter cio u si.

[C3]
   Nangmah na nawlbia sung bangin, Nihin ah hin, Na cabuai ah nang he
   kan i chawn, &quot;Mah hi nan tuah lai, Keimah philhlonak ah&quot; Na rak timi kha
   kan ruat than.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>208</hymn_number>
</song>